\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1942, he joined the Palmach, the elite strike force of the Haganah, the clandestine military organisation of the Jewish community in Palestine.\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3877, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3754, \"end\": 3761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palmach\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Palmach\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palmach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palmach\"}, {\"begin\": 3793, \"end\": 3800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haganah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Haganah\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haganah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haganah\"}, {\"begin\": 3847, \"end\": 3853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9999999999654392, \"rank\": 3.275021767199341e-11, \"text\": \"Jewish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}, {\"begin\": 3867, \"end\": 3876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandatory_Palestine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1514969220734484e-23, \"text\": \"Palestine\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandatory_Palestine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mandatory_Palestine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the elite strike force\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3785}, {\"ngram\": \"the clandestine military organisation\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1946, the British arrested Zamir for his involvement in bringing illegal immigrants to Palestine and imprisoned him at the Latrun jail.\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 4016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3891, \"end\": 3898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Army\", \"score\": 0.8371588790848012, \"rank\": 0.1945145682409797